<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/34619705">有哪些广受球迷恶搞的足球运动员?</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="6054322" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">如赫斯基，切尔西时期的托雷斯等。</div>


</div>
